      <title>美国银行将牵头为航空运输部门交易提供 18.3 亿美元杠杆贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/bofa-to-lead-1-83-billion-leveraged-loan-for-carrier-unit-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，美国银行公司已承诺为 Lone Star Funds 收购 Carrier Global Corp. 的商业和住宅消防部门提供 18.3 亿美元的杠杆贷款。由于信息属于保密，这些知情人士不愿透露姓名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/bofa-to-lead-1-83-billion-leveraged-loan-for-carrier-unit-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 00:21:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿里巴巴加入港股通或将为海外股票带来利好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/alibaba-s-connect-membership-may-be-a-boon-for-overseas-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿里巴巴集团控股有限公司即将加入沪港通，这可能会为全球市场带来高达 32 亿美元的资金。分析师表示，日本和美国股市是潜在的受益者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/alibaba-s-connect-membership-may-be-a-boon-for-overseas-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 00:17:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Seven & I 股价因收购后采取保护措施的消息而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/seven-i-dips-on-news-of-protective-steps-after-buyout-approach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前有消息称，7-Eleven 便利店运营商希望日本政府将其指定级别改为一个可能给 Alimentation Couche-Tard Inc. 推进收购提议设置潜在障碍的类别，随后，Seven &amp; i Holdings Co. 的股价在东京早盘交易中一度下跌 3.8%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/seven-i-dips-on-news-of-protective-steps-after-buyout-approach</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 00:06:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穆迪因美国调查成本将道明银行的评级展望调整为负面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/td-s-outlook-changed-to-negative-by-moody-s-on-cost-of-us-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国对多伦多道明银行洗钱控制调查的成本不断上升，给这家全球最强大的银行之一的信用评级蒙上了一层阴影，穆迪评级跟随竞争对手，对该银行给出了负面展望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/td-s-outlook-changed-to-negative-by-moody-s-on-cost-of-us-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 00:03:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
