      <title>印度一级市场蓬勃发展，吸引资金远离高价股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/booming-india-primary-market-lures-funds-away-from-pricey-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度新股发行的持续热潮引起了全球基金的兴趣，他们似乎因为印度的二级市场估值过高而避开了印度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/booming-india-primary-market-lures-funds-away-from-pricey-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
